No, you don't 
 understand.

20:15.200 --> 20:16.800
I hate closed places.

20:18.160 --> 20:20.080
It's the room 
 that scares me.

20:23.320 --> 20:24.760
Reed!

20:24.760 --> 20:26.600
It's an illusion!

