I can't! I can't!

20:34.200 --> 20:37.080
You've got to! Face 
 your fear, Nonnie!

20:37.080 --> 20:38.240
Face your fear!

20:38.240 --> 20:39.320
I can't!

20:39.320 --> 20:42.360
Face your fear! 
 It can't get you!

