You're a nightmare!

21:25.840 --> 21:27.520
I don't believe 
 in you!

21:27.520 --> 21:29.480
Reed, help me!

21:30.600 --> 21:31.560
Aah!

21:31.560 --> 21:33.840
You're not gonna 
 own me anymore!

21:44.760 --> 21:45.800
Nonnie.

21:45.800 --> 21:47.520
Nonnie!

21:52.280 --> 21:54.200
You OK?

